'''克莉絲汀娜·蕾妮·韓翠克絲'''（{{lang-en|Christina Rene Hendricks}}，{{bd|1975年|5月3日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]女演員，知名於[[AMC_(電視頻道)|AMC]]電視劇《[[廣告狂人|廣告狂人]]》（2007年至2015年）中飾演的{{le|瓊·霍洛威|Joan Holloway}}，藉此提名了六項[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]。

據《[[君子雜誌|君子雜誌]]》的女性讀者調查，韓翠克絲在該雜誌上獲選為「世界最性感的女人」<ref name="esquireApril20" />。2010年，她被《君子雜誌》評為最上相的美國女性<ref name="esquireApril20">{{cite web |title= The Esquire Survey of the American Woman |url= http://www.esquire.com/women/women-issue/survey-of-american-women-0510/ |publisher= Esquire |date= 2010-04-20 |accessdate= 2011-05-28 |archive-date= 2015-01-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150109231108/http://www.esquire.com/women/women-issue/survey-of-american-women-0510 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last= Welles |first= Denmark |url= http://www.thefirstpost.co.uk/62338,people,entertainment,christina-hendricks-voted-best-looking-woman-in-us-esquire-mad-men |title= Mad Men's Christina Hendricks voted best-looking woman in US | People |work= The First Post |date= 2010-04-23 |accessdate= 2011-02-20 |archive-date= 2011-08-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110808123730/http://www.thefirstpost.co.uk/62338,people,entertainment,christina-hendricks-voted-best-looking-woman-in-us-esquire-mad-men |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

韓翠克絲所參演過的電影包括《[[落日車神|落日車神]]》（2011年）、《{{le|上帝的口袋|God's Pocket (film)}}》（2014年）和《[[遺落流域|遺落流域]]》（2014年）。2015年起，她開始於電視劇《[[流金歲月_(美國電視劇)|流金歲月]]》中飾演席琳／椅子一角，並於2016年在《{{le|海普與雷納德 (電視劇)|Hap and Leonard (TV series)|海普與雷納德}}》中飾演楚蒂。

== 早期生活 ==
克莉絲汀娜·韓翠克絲出生於[[田納西州|田納西州]][[諾克斯維爾|諾克斯維爾]]<ref name="birth_place">{{cite web |title= Christina Hendricks |url= https://www.biography.com/people/christina-hendricks-17166486 |publisher= Biography.com |accessdate= 2017-07-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170504010556/http://www.biography.com/people/christina-hendricks-17166486 |archive-date= 2017-05-04 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。她的母親賈姬·蘇（娘家姓雷蒙）是名心理學家，而父親羅伯特·韓翠克絲在[[美國國家森林局|美國國家森林局]]工作，並來自於[[德國|德國]]的[[柏林|柏林]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-1388042/Christina-Hendricks-life-shaping-nicely-Im-learning-celebrate-I-born-with.html |title='I'm learning to celebrate what I was born with': Why life is shaping up nicely for Christina Hendricks |date=2011-05-24 |work=Daily Mail |accessdate=2017-07-03 |archive-date=2020-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213164557/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-1388042/Christina-Hendricks-life-shaping-nicely-Im-learning-celebrate-I-born-with.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= Christina Hendricks: a fine figure of a woman|url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/4269856/Christina-Hendricks-a-fine-figure-of-a-woman.html|accessdate= 2012-09-14|newspaper= The Telegraph|date= 2009-01-19|first= Catherine|last= Elsworth|archive-date= 2020-09-19|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200919004445/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/4269856/Christina-Hendricks-a-fine-figure-of-a-woman.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。由於她父親的緣故，使她擁有著美國和德國的國籍<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2011/sep/16/christina-hendricks-drive-mad-men?INTCMP=SRCH |title=Mad Men and me: Christina Hendricks interview |first=Hadley |last=Freeman |work=The Guardian |date=2011-09-16 |location=London |issn=0261-3077 |oclc=60623878 |accessdate=2011-09-20 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912184920/https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2011/sep/16/christina-hendricks-drive-mad-men?INTCMP=SRCH |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的家庭因為父親職業的關係而搬過幾次家，使韓翠克絲的早年生活多半在[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]的[[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieweb.com/christina-hendricks-talks-all-star-superman/|work=MovieWeb|title=Christina Hendricks Talks All-Star Superman|date=2016-03|accessdate=2016-11-05|author=Orange, Alan|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204161923/https://movieweb.com/christina-hendricks-talks-all-star-superman/|dead-url=no}}</ref>與[[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]的[[特溫福爾斯|特溫福爾斯]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/t/r/e/Donald-J-Trent/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-0465.html |title=DONALD J. TRENT FAMILY HISTORY:Information about Christina Rene Hendricks |publisher=genealogy.com |accessdate=2013-06-03 |archive-date=2014-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017181743/http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/t/r/e/Donald-J-Trent/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-0465.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>度過。

當韓翠克絲在6歲時，她們家搬到了[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]的[[費爾法克斯_(維吉尼亞州)|費爾法克斯]]，在那裡她就讀了{{le|費爾法克斯高中 (維吉尼亞州)|Fairfax High School (Fairfax, Virginia)|費爾法克斯高中}}<ref>{{cite news |first=John |last=Kelly |date=2014-09-23 |title=Christina Hendricks hated Fairfax High. Today’s students say she wouldn’t now. |newspaper=The Washington Post |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/christina-hendricks-hated-fairfax-high-todays-students-say-she-wouldnt-now/2014/09/22/8d41a79a-3dd0-11e4-b0ea-8141703bbf6f_story.html |accessdate=2016-06-13 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914202835/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/christina-hendricks-hated-fairfax-high-todays-students-say-she-wouldnt-now/2014/09/22/8d41a79a-3dd0-11e4-b0ea-8141703bbf6f_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據韓翠克絲所述，她在高中常被欺負並被稱作「流浪者（outcast）」和「[[哥德次文化|哥德]]（goth）」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/9088143/Christina-Hendricks-I-was-bullied-at-school-for-being-a-goth.html|work=The Telegraph|title=Christina Hendricks: 'I was bullied at school for being a goth'|date=2012-02-27|accessdate=2016-09-05|author=Wardrop, Murray|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109025048/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/9088143/Christina-Hendricks-I-was-bullied-at-school-for-being-a-goth.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在參加《[[17_(美國雜誌)|17]]》的雜誌封面競賽後，18歲的她和{{le|模特兒經紀公司|Modeling agency}}簽約，並搬到了[[紐約市|紐約市]]<ref>{{cite news |first=Elizabeth |last=Day |date=2014-08-03 |title=Christina Hendricks: 'My agency dropped me when I first agreed to play Joan in Mad Men' |newspaper=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2014/aug/03/christina-hendricks-joan-mad-men-gods-pocket-interview |accessdate=2016-06-13 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000755/http://www.theguardian.com/culture/2014/aug/03/christina-hendricks-joan-mad-men-gods-pocket-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 職業生涯 ==
韓翠克絲於[[特溫福爾斯|特溫福爾斯]]的兒童音樂劇中演出而開始她的職業生涯。18歲至27歲間，她在[[音樂電視網|MTV]]的[[詩選劇|詩選劇]]《{{le|基情二加一|Undressed}}》中演出，這也是她首次參演的影視作品。而她的第一個主要角色是在《{{le|乞丐與選擇者|Beggars and Choosers (TV series)}}》中所飾演的凱莉一角<ref>{{IMDb character|0160936|Kelly Kramer}}</ref>。此後，她又出演了《{{le|法院 (電視劇)|The Court (TV series)|法院}}》和《''The Big Time''》（電視電影），以及在[[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]的{{le|科布堡 (奧克拉荷馬州)|Fort Cobb, Oklahoma|科布堡}}拍攝的法律劇《{{le|律師奶爸|Kevin Hill}}》。此外，韓翠克絲還在知名的醫學劇《[[急診室的春天|急診室的春天]]》和科幻劇《[[螢火蟲_(電視劇)|螢火蟲]]》中擔任過重要角色。2007年，她在由[[基普·帕杜|基普·帕杜]]主演的電影《{{le|碧可南部|South of Pico}}》中擔任配角。2007年至2008年間，她在[[全国广播公司|NBC]]電視劇《{{le|重返重案組|Life (U.S. TV series)}}》中飾演常駐角色奧莉維亞·坎頓。此外，她還出演了{{le|殘鐘樂團|Broken Bells}}的[[MV|MV]]「{{le|Broken Bells (專輯)|Broken Bells (album)|Broken Bells}}」<ref>{{cite web |last=Avalos |first=Steven |url=http://www.popeater.com/2010/06/02/christina-hendricks-broken-bells-music-video/ |title=Christina Hendricks Stars in Broken Bells Music Video |publisher=[[赫芬頓郵報|PopEater]] |date=2010-06-02 |accessdate=2011-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028204210/http://www.popeater.com/2010/06/02/christina-hendricks-broken-bells-music-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和{{le|超清晰樂團|Everclear (band)}}的MV「One Hit Wonder」<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Best-Looking Woman’ Christina Hendricks is a Music Video Star|url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/stop-the-presses/best-looking-woman-christina-hendricks-is-a-music-video-star.html|publisher={{le|雅虎音樂|Yahoo! Music|Yahoo! Music}}|date=2010-06-02|accessdate=2012-09-29|archive-date=2013-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216165846/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/stop-the-presses/best-looking-woman-christina-hendricks-is-a-music-video-star.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年起，韓翠克絲開始在[[AMC_(電視頻道)|AMC]]電視劇《[[廣告狂人|廣告狂人]]》中飾演{{le|瓊·霍洛威|Joan Holloway}}，是一名冷酷的女管理秘書。韓翠克絲的演出獲得了極高的評價，並也因此於2007年至2015年間獲得了[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]六項的提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2015/outstanding-supporting-actress-in-a-drama-series |title=Nominees/Winners | Television Academy |publisher={{le|電視藝術和科學學院|Academy of Television Arts & Sciences|Academy of Television Arts & Sciences}} |accessdate=2017-05-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114011/https://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/2015/outstanding-supporting-actress-in-a-drama-series |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年，她在由[[尼可拉·溫丁·黑芬|尼可拉·溫丁·黑芬]]執導的驚悚片《[[落日車神|落日車神]]》中演出，並與[[嘉莉·慕萊根|嘉莉·慕萊根]]及[[瑞恩·高斯林|瑞恩·高斯林]]主演<ref>{{cite web |last=Helyer |first=Rachel |url=http://www.thefirstpost.co.uk/68437,people,news,mad-men-christina-hendricks-eyes-big-screen-roles-drive |title=Mad Men's Hendricks eyes big-screen roles |work=The First Post |date=2010-09-09 |accessdate=2013-06-03 |archive-date=2010-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100912204207/http://www.thefirstpost.co.uk/68437,people,news,mad-men-christina-hendricks-eyes-big-screen-roles-drive |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，她在瑞恩·高斯林的導演處女作《[[遺落流域|遺落流域]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=Cannes 2014: The bafflement of Ryan Gosling's 'Lost River|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-cannes-2014-ryan-gosling-lost-river-20140521-story.html|publisher=The LA Times|accessdate=2014-06-07|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919065716/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-cannes-2014-ryan-gosling-lost-river-20140521-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>中擔任主角，並於2015年與[[莎莉·賽隆|莎莉·賽隆]]、[[克蘿伊·摩蕾茲|克蘿伊·摩蕾茲]]共同參演《[[暗處|暗處]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=Dark Places|url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/91742/dark-places-international-one-sheet-laid/|publisher=Dread Central|accessdate=2014-06-07|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924090624/https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/91742/dark-places-international-one-sheet-laid/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，韓翠克絲再次與黑芬合作，在驚悚片《[[霓虹惡魔|霓虹惡魔]]》中演出<ref>{{cite web|title=Keanu Reeves, Christina Hendricks Join Refn’s ‘The Neon Demon’|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3331132/keanu-reeves-christina-hendricks-join-refns-neon-demon/|publisher=Variety|accessdate=2014-06-07|archive-date=2015-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205194246/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3331132/keanu-reeves-christina-hendricks-join-refns-neon-demon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年9月，宣布她將出演懸疑電影《{{le|怪屋 (電影)|Crooked House (film)|怪屋}}》，該片改編自[[阿嘉莎·克莉絲蒂|阿嘉莎·克莉絲蒂]]的小說《[[怪屋|怪屋]]》<ref name="CrookedHouse">{{Cite web |url=http://m.screendaily.com/5109411.article/ |title=Agatha Christie thriller 'Crooked House' underway |last=Wiseman |first=Andreas |date=2016-09-13 |website=Screen Daily |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archive-date=2016-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921070054/http://m.screendaily.com/5109411.article/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 文化影響 ==
[[File:Christina_Hendricks_2012.jpg|thumb]]]]
韓翠克絲被英國議員{{le|琳恩·費瑟史東|Lynne Featherstone}}認為是理想的{{le|女性身材|Female body shape}}，她認為韓翠克絲的沙漏型是女性所嚮往的形象，她說：「克莉絲汀娜·韓翠克絲絕對是神話般的...我們需要更多這樣的榜樣。當有一個曲線玲瓏的好榜樣時，這不應該是如此不尋常的。」<ref name="BBCjuly27">{{cite news|title=Does Christina Hendricks have a body women should aspire to|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-10760903|newspaper=BBC News Magazine|accessdate=2011-05-28|date=2010-06-27|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109001752/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-10760903|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的電視評論家瑪莉·麥克納馬拉說，她對瓊（{{le|瓊·霍洛威|Joan Holloway}}）的描寫徹底改變了對電視美女的看法<ref>{{cite news |last= Geoghegan |first= Tom |title= Does Christina Hendricks have a body women should aspire to? |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-10760903 |accessdate= 2011-05-28 |newspaper= BBC News Magazine |date= 2010-06-27 |archive-date= 2020-11-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201109001752/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-10760903 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2011年，韓翠克絲被稱為「新現代理想的好萊塢魅力，充滿著幻想、妖艷，就像回到[[瑪麗蓮·夢露|瑪麗蓮·夢露]]、[[珍·羅素|珍·羅素]]和[[維若妮卡·蕾克|維若妮卡·蕾克]]的時日」<ref>{{cite web |last= Kiley |first= David |title= Mad Men Star Christina Hendricks The New Face of Vivienne Westwood |url= http://www.luxist.com/2011/03/02/mad-men-star-christina-hendricks-the-new-face-of-vivienne-westwo/ |publisher= luxist.com |accessdate= 2011-05-28 |date= 2011-03-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110506132019/http://www.luxist.com/2011/03/02/mad-men-star-christina-hendricks-the-new-face-of-vivienne-westwo/ |archive-date= 2011-05-06 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>；英國設計師[[薇薇安·魏斯伍德|薇薇安·魏斯伍德]]將其她描述為「美的化身」<ref>{{cite news|title=Christina Hendricks launches Vivienne Westwood's new jewellery line... but who's looking at her tiara?|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1362039/Christina-Hendricks-launches-Vivienne-Westwoods-new-jewellery-line.html|accessdate=2011-05-28|newspaper=Daily Mail Online|date=2011-03-02|location=London|archive-date=2017-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226214206/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1362039/Christina-Hendricks-launches-Vivienne-Westwoods-new-jewellery-line.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英國美容[[整形|整形]]外科醫師協會的一項研究發現，2010年的英國女性接受[[隆胸|隆胸]]手術的人數上升了10％，其中部分是受到韓翠克絲的影響<ref name=lusher20110130>{{cite news|last=Lusher|first=Adam|title=Mad Men star Christina Hendricks sparks rush for breast implants|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/health/healthnews/8290407/Mad-Men-star-Christina-Hendricks-sparks-rush-for-breast-implants.html|accessdate=2011-01-31|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|date=2011-01-30|location=London|archive-date=2014-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140721212736/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/health/healthnews/8290407/Mad-Men-star-Christina-Hendricks-sparks-rush-for-breast-implants.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

韓翠克絲已不再接受「豐滿」這一形容詞，並曾抨擊在採訪時使用這詞的記者<ref>{{cite news|title=Hollywood's voluptuous beauty was offended? Go (full) figure …|url=http://www.smh.com.au/lifestyle/fashion/hollywoods-voluptuous-beauty-was-offended-go-full-figure-8230-20121013-27jp5.html|accessdate=2012-10-14|newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2012-10-14|location=Sydney|archive-date=2012-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014103524/http://www.smh.com.au/lifestyle/fashion/hollywoods-voluptuous-beauty-was-offended-go-full-figure-8230-20121013-27jp5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。韓翠克絲在2010年9月表示，媒體過分關注女性的身體，而不是她們本身，「我在片中（《廣告狂人》）努力工作，然後所有人都在談論是我的身體。」<ref>{{cite news |last= Hunter |first= Aina |title= Christina Hendricks' Measurements: Naked "I Look Like a Woman" |url= http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504763_162-20009422-10391704.html |accessdate= 2011-05-28 |date= 2010-06 |publisher= CBS News |archive-date= 2013-05-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130517082209/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504763_162-20009422-10391704.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= http://showbiz.sky.com/christinas-body-rant | title= Christina's body comments | publisher= Sky Showbiz | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100905175036/http://showbiz.sky.com/christinas-body-rant | archivedate= 2010-09-05 | accessdate= 2017-07-03 }}</ref>

== 個人生活 ==
韓翠克絲天生有著一頭金髮，10歲時，因《[[清秀佳人|清秀佳人]]》的啟發而將頭髮染紅。她認為這樣的扮相較符合《[[廣告狂人|廣告狂人]]》中的{{le|瓊·霍洛威|Joan Holloway}}一角<ref name="lat20100701">{{cite web |date= 2010-07-01 |author= Katie Hintz-Zambrano |title= Christina Hendricks Dazzles on LA Times Magazine |url= http://www.stylelist.com/2010/07/01/christina-hendricks-la-times-magazine/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100704083907/http://www.stylelist.com/2010/07/01/christina-hendricks-la-times-magazine/ |archivedate= 2010-07-04 |publisher= AOL |work= stylelist.com |accessdate= 2010-06-15 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2009年10月11日，她與演員{{le|傑弗利·阿蘭德|Geoffrey Arend}}結婚<ref name=P>{{cite web|title=Christina Hendricks Marries in New York|first=Elaine|last=Aradillas|date=2009-10-11|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20311577,00.html|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424033206/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20311577,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在受訪時表示，她和丈夫並不會想要孩子<ref>{{cite web|title=Mad Men Christina Hendricks doesn't want children|date=2014-10-11|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2602718/Mad-Mens-Christina-Hendricks-doesnt-want-children.html|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305093751/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2602718/Mad-Mens-Christina-Hendricks-doesnt-want-children.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

